HEADWORD: Zingiberaceous
<hw>Zin`gi*ber*a"ceous</hw>
<pr>(z⟦icr⟧n`j⟦icr⟧*b⟦etil⟧r*⟦amac⟧"sh⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>zingiber</ets> ginger. See <er>Ginger</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to ginger, or to a tribe
(<spn>Zingibereae</spn>) of endogenous plants of the order
<ord>Scitamineae</ord>. See <er>Scitamineous</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

